@startuml seq_22_report_violation
title Sequence Diagram: UC-22 Report Violation

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Report Controller" as Controller
participant "Report Service" as Service
participant "Report Repo" as Repo
participant "Target Repo" as TargetRepo

User -> Frontend: (1.1/2.1/3.1) Fill report form & Submit
Frontend -> Controller: (3.2) POST /api/reports {target_id, type, reason}
Controller -> Service: (4.1) Create Report
Service -> TargetRepo: (4.2) Validate target exists (Post/Comment/Community)
TargetRepo --> Service: (4.3) Target is valid

Service -> Repo: (5.1/6.1) Create Report record (Status: Pending)
Repo --> Service: (5.2/6.2) Report created
Service --> Controller: (7.1) Success
Controller --> Frontend: (7.2) 201 Created
Frontend --> User: (7.3) Show "Report submitted" message
@enduml
